5: You're in a good mood, Alk.
9:
Of course I am! Who wouldn't be
after getting perfectly marbled
meat on sale? Ahhh... What should I
make?
17:
Heya, Nimbus! Your cute girlfriend
not with you today?
23:
Why so shy? You were walking
around all lovey-dovey together the
other day! Man, I can't wait to
graduate from the single life too!
25:
Gotta say though, I never expected
that kinda girl would be your type.
31:
N-not that I mean anything bad by
that! I swear!
34:
I'm not mad, just confused. What do
you mean you saw me with my
girlfriend? I don't have one.
36:
What? But... I know what I saw.
You've been going everywhere with
her hanging off your arm.
38:
That can't have been me. But then
who—
48:
Fancy meeting you here! We've
gotta be bound by fate, don'tcha
think? Sounds to me like we should
just tie the knot—
53:
In your dreams! What the hell've you
been doing? There're these weird
rumors floating around—
63: ...Am I the only one seeing double?!
72:
Ehehe, don't be mean! He's
obviously the result of the love
between us!
78: You two had a child together?!
84:
Obviously not, dumbass! That ain't
no kid!
88:
...Mind giving us a more thorough
explanation, Sohvi?
91:
Is it that hard to put two and two
together? I took Nimbus's molted fur
and made a life-sized plushie out of
it!
101:
A plushie that can speak too.
Impressive.
105: Scary, is what I'd call it.
109:
Remember how I was working on a
revival concoction before meeting
Nimbus? I just put that research to
use and imbued this vessel with a
mock life force.
113:
Sohvi. I love you. Marry me, my
darling.
118:
Ugh, hearing my own voice say
gross crap like that gives me the
creeps! That's it! I'm ripping this
thing apart!
123:
No! Nimbus, you meanie! You can't
do that to my masterpiece!
128:
Watch me! No way I can turn a blind
eye to this cursed doll!
139: I get it! Ehe! Hehehe! You're jealous!
146: Of a plushie too! That's so cuuute!
156:
You don't have to be shy about it! I
love seeing this side of you!
162:
You're not seeing ANYTHING but your
own DELUSIONS!
166:
But I'll be nice and get rid of this
thing if it's making you that jealous!
Teehee!
186:
This is starting to look like the scene
of a murder...
196:
Hot... Don't want... to die... Help... He...
Ah...
201:
Watching my face get burned to a
crisp... Can't say I've ever had the
displeasure of experiencing this
before.
205:
So, uh... Nimbus? Mind if I ask you
something?
206:
You think we could, uh, skip out on
meat for dinner tonight? I'm feeling
kinda queasy...
210:
Yeah, that... That sounds like a good
idea.
